The remaining fixtures in Match Day 1 of the Champions League, will be played on Wednesday across Europe. Paris Saint-Germain take on Real Madrid, in what promises to be a mouthwatering clash. Last year’s runners-up Tottenham Hotspur travel to Olympiacos and Shakhtar Donetsk welcome Manchester City. Atletico Madrid will also play Juventus, while Club Brugge host Galatasaray. Wednesday, September 18
GROUP A
FT: Club Brugge 0 vs Galatasaray 0
FT: Paris Saint-Germain 3 vs Real Madrid 0 GROUP B
FT: Olympiacos 2 vs Tottenham Hotspur 2
FT: FC Bayern München 3 vs FK Crvena Zvezda 0 GROUP C
FT: Dinamo Zagreb 4 vs Atalanta 0
FT: Shakhtar Donetsk 0 vs Manchester City 3 GROUP D
FT: Atletico Madrid 2 vs Juventus 2
